Package com.kuka.jogging.provider

Package contains common jogging provider api.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICartesianJoggingSupport
    This interface enables the implementing class to support cartesian jogging.
    IJoggingSupport
    Interface which enables the implementing class to set a timeout for jogging motions.
    IJointJoggingSupport
    This interface enables the implementing class to support joint jogging.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CartesianJoggingData
    Runtime data for cartesian jogging.
    CartesianMouseJoggingData
    Runtime data for cartesian Mouse controlled jogging.
    CartesianVelocityData
    The velocity data for Cartesian movement.
    JointJoggingData
    Runtime data for joint specific jogging.
